@page "/support"
@layout EmptyLayout

<div class="support-page">
    <div class="support-container">
        <div class="support-header">
            <div class="support-logo">LifeAlert +</div>
            <p class="support-tagline">We're here to help</p>
        </div>

        <div class="support-content">
            <h2 class="section-title">Support</h2>
            <p>We are here to help you ensure that your LifeAlertPlus system works reliably and efficiently.</p>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">Contact Us</h3>
            <p>If you experience any issues with the application or the IoT device, please contact our support team:</p>
            <p class="contact-email">Email: <a href="mailto:support@lifealertplusiot.com">support&#64;lifealertplusiot.com</a></p>
            <p>We aim to respond to all inquiries as soon as possible.</p>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">Before Contacting Support</h3>
            <p>To resolve common issues quickly, please check the following:</p>
            <ul class="check-list">
                <li>Make sure the device is properly charged</li>
                <li>Restart the device</li>
                <li>Verify that the device has an active internet connection</li>
                <li>Ensure the application is up to date</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">Common Issues</h3>

            <div class="issue-card">
                <h4>Device not sending data</h4>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Check battery level</li>
                    <li>Restart the device</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="issue-card">
                <h4>Application not loading data</h4>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Refresh the page</li>
                    <li>Check internet connection</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="issue-card">
                <h4>Login or authentication issues</h4>
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>Reset your password</li>
                    <li>Ensure your email is verified</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">Technical Support</h3>
            <p>For technical inquiries or system-related issues, please include:</p>
            <ul class="check-list">
                <li>A description of the problem</li>
                <li>Steps to reproduce the issue</li>
                <li>Screenshots (if available)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="contact-email">Email: <a href="mailto:support@lifealertplusiot.com">support&#64;lifealertplusiot.com</a></p>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">Automated Emails</h3>
            <p>Please note that system-generated messages (account verification, password reset, notifications) are sent from:</p>
            <p class="contact-email"><a href="mailto:noreply@lifealertplusiot.com">noreply&#64;lifealertplusiot.com</a></p>
            <p>This address is not monitored for incoming messages.</p>

            <div class="notice-box">
                <h3 class="subsection-title">Service Notice</h3>
                <p>LifeAlertPlus is designed to assist monitoring and alerting but does not guarantee prevention of incidents. Always rely on emergency services in critical situations.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="support-footer">
            <a class="back-link" href="/dashboard">← Back to Dashboard</a>
            <a class="back-link" href="/about">About Us</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
